in my fucking bar.

198
00:17:17.920 --> 00:17:21.057
so it's my fucking drink. Ben.

199
00:17:21.161 --> 00:17:23.541
Uh. it's Brett. Brett.

200
00:17:26.195 --> 00:17:29.195
