Charlotte.

216
00:18:27.679 --> 00:18:28.886
Charlotte?

217
00:18:28.989 --> 00:18:30.851
Finally!

218
00:18:30.955 --> 00:18:32.715
No. I'm joking! I'm
joking. No. no. it's...

