for my Instagram.

262
00:20:15.506 --> 00:20:20.610
Thank you for your offer. Ben.
but we don't want your money.

263
00:20:24.575 --> 00:20:26.679
Yeah. it's Brett.

264
00:20:26.782 --> 00:20:28.851
Yeah. it's Brett.

265
00:20:28.955 --> 00:20:31.437
