284
00:21:16.264 --> 00:21:18.024
Of course.

285
00:21:22.126 --> 00:21:23.851
Everything okay?

286
00:21:26.437 --> 00:21:28.024
Well...

287
00:21:28.126 --> 00:21:31.057
Brett can be a little
much sometimes.

288
