341
00:25:10.161 --> 00:25:12.230
Uh. one minute.

342
00:25:12.333 --> 00:25:13.195
Yes?

343
00:25:13.299 --> 00:25:15.057
Five minutes.

344
00:25:16.679 --> 00:25:17.920
